<div class="ability explanation">
	<div class="title">Abilities</div>
	<dl><dt><span><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/7ea00c46aa6b565d6054e18deab891fa2.png"></span><span>Experience's Boon III</span></dt><dd><div>Grants Ranzal an Attack Gauge and a Burst Gauge.<br>The Attack Gauge fills when regular attacks connect<br>with enemies, while the Burst Gauge is filled when<br>force strikes successfully connect.<br>For every completely filled gauge, Ranzal's defense<br>is increased. Any filled gauges are consumed when<br>using the Cyclone Blade skill, increasing its power.</div></dd><dt><span><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/1773f9fc2cee21b3daccbd539f0569eb2.png"></span><span>Relentless Spirit III</span></dt><dd><div>Reduces susceptibility to freeze and bog<br>by 100%. When Ranzal is hit by an attack<br>that would have inflicted freeze or bog on him,<br>his strength is increased by 15% for 10 seconds.<br>This increase will not stack, and, after activating,<br>this buff cannot be activated again by the same<br>affliction for 15 seconds.</div></dd><dt><span><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/318c94807552d34eb43eebac3f21952f2.png"></span><span>Skill Damage +35%</span></dt><dd><div>Increases attack skill damage by 35%.</div></dd></dl></div></div></div><div><br></div><div>Notes:</div><div>1. The stats shown here represent the adventurer at level 100 with 70 mana nodes unbound.</div><div>2. The stats shown here do not include increases or decreases due to abilities.</div><div>3. The stats for the adventurer included in this notification shown in any prior notifications or preview videos were the stats at level 80 with 50 mana nodes unbound.</div><div>4. When an adventurer&#39;s skill level increases, the skill gauge will fill more slowly when set as a shared skill.</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1618725600,update_time1618801086